cps.entities.models

Class DisabledCellsStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • cps.entities.models.DisabledCellsStatistics

  • public class DisabledCellsStatistics
extends java.lang.Object
    Records statistical data about enable/disable actions performed on Parking Cells (car storage inside of a parking lot). Allows calculating the number of disabled cells in a given period, and the amount of time during which cells were inactive.
